Cactus Code Thorn NPScalars_EM
Thorn Author(s)     : 
Thorn Maintainer(s) : 
--------------------------------------------------------------------------

Purpose of the thorn:
Implementation of the Newman-Penrose scalars 
$\Phi_{0}$, $\Phi_{1}$, $\Phi_{2}$ (electromagnetic radiation)
to extract radiation emitted in BH-EM spacetimes.

